parameters.name: R
parameters.description: Distance of Pioneer 11 from Saturn, in Saturn RADII (1 Saturn radii is 60401 KM).

parameters.name: LAT
parameters.description: Latitude of Pioneer 11 in an unknown, west longitude coordinates.

parameters.name: LON
parameters.description: Longitude of Pioneer 11 in an unknown, west longitude coordinates.

parameters.name: BR
parameters.description: Radial component of the magnetic field in RK coordinates, positive away from Saturn.

parameters.name: BTHETA
parameters.description: Polar component of the magnetic field in RK coordinates, positive northward.

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description: Azimuthal component of the magnetic field in RK coordinates, positive eastward.
